Set default formatting for "device type" properties
(overrides the static configuration of formatting)

Inputs:

- Prefix : STRING;

Prefix string for all "device type" properties

- Length : DINT;

Minimum length for configurated device type names
(completed with blank characters)
Left aligned if this length is less than 0

- Suffix : STRING;

Suffix string for all "device type" properties

Outputs:

- OK : BOOL;

True if successful
